# ─── Mongolbank Gold Price API ───────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# HOW TO FIND THE ENDPOINT (one-time setup):
#   1. Open Chrome → https://www.mongolbank.mn/mn/gold-and-silver-price
#   2. Open DevTools (F12) → Network tab → filter "Fetch/XHR"
#   3. Reload the page
#   4. Look for a request that returns JSON with fields like:
#        GOLD_BUY, RATE_DATE, SILVER_BUY
#   5. Right-click that request → Copy → Copy URL
#   6. Paste the FULL URL below as VITE_MB_GOLD_PATH (just the pathname + query)
#      e.g.  /api/v1/goldSilver?pageSize=5&pageNumber=1
#
# The Vite dev server proxies /mb-gold → mongolbank.mn{VITE_MB_GOLD_PATH}
# so you never hit CORS issues during development.
#
# In production: set up a Cloudflare Worker / Vercel serverless function that
# forwards /mb-gold requests to mongolbank.mn and adds CORS headers.
#
# Confirmed via Chrome DevTools on 2026-06-07:
VITE_MB_GOLD_PATH=/mn/gold-and-silver-price/data

# ─── Google Apps Script (for contact form) ───────────────────────────────────
VITE_GOOGLE_APPS_SCRIPT_URL=
